### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### ADMIN — Account+Roles creation + Dashboard analytics
### All endpoints require X-Admin-Key header
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


### Create account WITH roles in one atomic call (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts-with-roles
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}

{
  "accountName": "PayPal",
  "logoUrl": "https://logo.clearbit.com/paypal.com",
  "roles": [
    "Data Engineer",
    "Software Engineer",
    "Backend Developer"
  ]
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accountId", response.body.id);
  client.log("Created account: " + response.body.name + " | id: " + response.body.id);
%}


###


### Create another account — Ford
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts-with-roles
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}

{
  "accountName": "Ford",
  "logoUrl": "https://logo.clearbit.com/ford.com",
  "roles": [
    "Data Engineer",
    "DevOps Engineer",
    "Frontend Developer"
  ]
}


###


### Create another account — Google
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/accounts-with-roles
Content-Type: application/json
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}

{
  "accountName": "Google",
  "logoUrl": "https://logo.clearbit.com/google.com",
  "roles": [
    "Data Scientist",
    "Software Engineer",
    "ML Engineer"
  ]
}


###


### Dashboard — KPI summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard/summary
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}
Accept: application/json


###


### Dashboard — Sessions by week (last 8 weeks)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard/sessions-by-week
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}
Accept: application/json


###


### Dashboard — All users' performance (for admin table)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard/users/performance
X-Admin-Key: {{adminKey}}
Accept: application/json
